-action, as described in the scenario. This will be integrated into a Flask template.\n"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"f494cc60"},"source":["**Reasoning**:\n","The first instruction is to create a `static` directory inside `flask_portfolio_app` and a `style.css` file within it. I will use `os.makedirs` and `open` to achieve this, along with writing some initial CSS for the hero section.\n","\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"169520f9","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1772900570857,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":53,"user":{"displayName":"Nusrath Fathima","userId":"09146625910007660115"}},"outputId":"d84743cc-d510-4676-cefc-6ce06a9ac3f8"},"source":["import os\n","\n","static_dir = os.path.join(project_dir, 'static')\n","os.makedirs(static_dir, exist_ok=True)\n","\n","css_content = '''\n","body {\n","    margin: 0;\n","    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n","}\n","\n",".hero-section {\n","    background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/222222/FFFFFF?text=Hero+Background'); /* Placeholder image */\n","    background-size: cover;\n","    background-position: center;\n","    color: white;\n","    text-align: center;\n","    padding: 100px 20px;\n","    display: flex;\n","    flex-direction: column;\n","    justify-content: center;\n","    align-items: center;\n","    min-height: 80vh; /* Make hero section at least 80% of viewport height */\n","}\n","\n",".hero-section h1 {\n","    font-size: 3.5em;\n","    margin-bottom: 20px;\n","}\n","\n",".hero-section p {\n","    font-size: 1.5em;\n","    margin-bottom: 40px;\n","    max-width: 700px;\n","    line-height: 1.6;\n","}\n","\n",".hero-section .btn {\n","    background-color: #007bff; /* Call-to-action button color */\n","    color: white;\n","    padding: 15px 30px;\n","    text-decoration: none;\n","    border-radius: 5px;\n","    font-size: 1.2em;\n","    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n","}\n","\n",".hero-section .btn:hover {\n","    background-color: #0056b3;\n","}\n","'''\n","\n","with open(os.path.join(static_dir, 'style.css'), 'w') as f:\n","    f.write(css_content)\n","\n","print(f\"Created static directory: {static_dir}/\")\n","print(f\"Created style.css inside {static_dir}/\")\n"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Created static directory: flask_portfolio_app/static/\n","Created style.css inside flask_portfolio_app/static/\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"e102dc07"},"source":["**Reasoning**:\n","I will create the `index.html` file in the `templates` directory with the hero section HTML and then write the necessary Flask code into `app.py` to render this template. This addresses instructions 3, 4, and 5 of the subtask.\n","\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"73144cf1","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1772900579877,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":23,"user":{"displayName":"Nusrath Fathima","userId":"09146625910007660115"}},"outputId":"bdd032b3-8223-4d0a-d051-ad3251962644"},"source":["import os\n","\n","# Create index.html content\n","html_content = '''\n","<!DOCTYPE html>\n","<html lang=\"en\">\n","<head>\n","    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n","    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n","    <title>Portfolio Website</title>\n","    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"{{ url_for('static', filename='style.css') }}\">\n","</head>\n","<body>\n","    <section class=\"hero-section\">\n","        <h1>Hello, I'm a Freelance Designer</h1>\n","        <p>Crafting beautiful and functional web experiences for clients worldwide. Let's create something amazing together.</p>\n","        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"btn\">Get in Touch</a>\n","    </section>\n","</body>\n","</html>\n","'''\n","\n","# Write index.html to templates directory\n","with open(os.path.join(templates_dir, 'index.html'), 'w') as f:\n","    f.write(html_content)\n","\n","print(f\"Created index.html inside {templates_dir}/\")\n","\n","# Create app.py content\n","app_py_content = '''\n","from flask import Flask, render_template\n","\n","app = Flask(__name__)\n","\n","@app.route('/')\n","def home():\n","    return render_template('index.html')\n","\n","if __name__ == '__main__':\n","    app.run(debug=True)\n","'''\n","\n","# Write app.py content\n","with open(os.path.join(project_dir, 'app.py'), 'w') as f:\n","    f.write(app_py_content)\n","\n","print(f\"Updated app.py inside {project_dir}/\")"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Created index.html inside flask_portfolio_app/templates/\n","Updated app.py inside flask_portfolio_app/\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"be27092e"},"source":["### Verification Step: Run the Flask Application\n","\n","To verify that the hero section has been successfully integrated, navigate to the `flask_portfolio_app` directory in your terminal and run the `app.py` file. Then, open your web browser and go to `http://127.0.0.1:5000/` (or the address provided by Flask if running in a different environment like Colab).\n","\n","```bash\n","cd flask_portfolio_app\n","python app.py\n","```\n","\n","You should see the hero section displayed in your browser."]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"824bfabe"},"source":["## Create Portfolio Gallery\n","\n","### Subtask:\n","Develop a responsive portfolio gallery in a clean grid layout, as specified, using HTML and CSS. This section will be designed to showcase project examples.\n"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"40a511b8"},"source":["**Reasoning**:\n","I will append the CSS rules for the portfolio gallery to the existing `style.css` file and add the HTML structure for the portfolio gallery section to the `index.html` file, including placeholder project items, to meet the subtask requirements.\n","\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"23751671","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1772900607849,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":57,"user":{"displayName":"Nusrath Fathima","userId":"09146625910007660115"}},"outputId":"892da38a-7ee4-4a8c-f6c3-580b1a32d8d8"},"source":["import os\n","\n","# Define CSS for the portfolio gallery\n","portfolio_css = '''\n",".portfolio-section {\n","    padding: 60px 20px;\n","    text-align: center;\n","    background-color: #f8f9fa;\n","}\n","\n",".portfolio-section h2 {\n","    font-size: 2.5em;\n","    margin-bottom: 40px;\n","    color: #333;\n","}\n","\n",".portfolio-grid {\n","    display: grid;\n","    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n","    gap: 30px;\n","    max-width: 1200px;\n","    margin: 0 auto;\n","}\n","\n",".portfolio-item {\n","    background-color: white;\n","    border-radius: 8px;\n","    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n","    overflow: hidden;\n","    text-align: left;\n","    transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n","}\n","\n",".portfolio-item:hover {\n","    transform: translateY(-5px);\n","}\n","\n",".portfolio-item img {\n","    width: 100%;\n","    height: 200px;\n","    object-fit: cover;\n","    display: block;\n","}\n","\n",".portfolio-item-info {\n","    padding: 20px;\n","}\n","\n",".portfolio-item-info h3 {\n","    font-size: 1.5em;\n","    margin-top: 0;\n","    margin-bottom: 10px;\n","    color: #007bff;\n","}\n","\n",".portfolio-item-info p {\n","    font-size: 1em;\n","    color: #666;\n","    line-height: 1.5;\n","}\n","\n","/* Responsive adjustments */\n","@media (max-width: 768px) {\n","    .hero-section h1 {\n","        font-size: 2.5em;\n","    }\n","    .hero-section p {\n","        font-size: 1.2em;\n","    }\n","    .portfolio-grid {\n","        grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n","    }\n","}\n","'''\n","\n","# Define HTML for the portfolio gallery\n","portfolio_html = '''\n","    <section class=\"portfolio-section\">\n","        <h2>My Portfolio</h2>\n","        <div class=\"portfolio-grid\">\n","            <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n","                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/FF5733/FFFFFF?text=Project+1\" alt=\"Project 1\">\n","                <div class=\"portfolio-item-info\">\n","                    <h3>Project Title 1</h3>\n","                    <p>A description of the first project, highlighting key features and technologies used.</p>\n","                </div>\n","            </div>\n","            <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n","                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/33FF57/FFFFFF?text=Project+2\" alt=\"Project 2\">\n","                <div class=\"portfolio-item-info\">\n","                    <h3>Project Title 2</h3>\n","                    <p>Details about the second project, showcasing its impact and creative solutions.</p>\n","                </div>\n","            </div>\n","            <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n","                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/3357FF/FFFFFF?text=Project+3\" alt=\"Project 3\">\n","                <div class=\"portfolio-item-info\">\n","                    <h3>Project Title 3</h3>\n","                    <p>An overview of the third project, emphasizing design principles and user experience.</p>\n","                </div>\n","            </div>\n","            <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n","                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x200/FF33CC/FFFFFF?text=Project+4\" alt=\"Project 4\">\n","                <div class=\"portfolio-item-info\">\n","                    <h3>Project Title 4</h3>\n","                    <p>Explanation of the fourth project, including challenges faced and how they were overcome.</p>\n","                </div>\n","            </div>\n","        </div>\n","    </section>\n","'''\n","\n","# Append CSS to style.css\n","style_css_path = os.path.join(project_dir, 'static', 'style.css')\n","with open(style_css_path, 'a') as f:\n","    f.write(portfolio_css)\n","\n","print(f\"Appended portfolio gallery CSS to {style_css_path}\")\n","\n","# Read existing index.html content\n","index_html_path = os.path.join(project_dir, 'templates', 'index.html')\n","with open(index_html_path, 'r') as f:\n","    html_content = f.read()\n","\n","# Insert portfolio HTML before the closing </body> tag\n","# Ensure there's a body tag to replace, otherwise just append (though it should exist)\n","if '</body>' in html_content:\n","    updated_html_content = html_content.replace('</body>', portfolio_html + '\\n</body>')\n","else:\n","    updated_html_content = html_content + portfolio_html # Fallback if no body tag (unlikely)\n","\n","# Write updated index.html\n","with open(index_html_path, 'w') as f:\n","    f.write(updated_html_content)\n","\n","print(f\"Appended portfolio gallery HTML to {index_html_path}\")\n"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Appended portfolio gallery CSS to flask_portfolio_app/static/style.css\n","Appended portfolio gallery HTML to flask_portfolio_app/templates/index.html\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"9fdafcfa"},"source":["## Build About Section\n","\n","### Subtask:\n","Generate the HTML and CSS for an 'About Me' section to present the designer’s professional bio in a compelling manner.\n"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"f351e06f"},"source":["**Reasoning**:\n","I will append the CSS rules for the 'About Me' section to the existing `style.css` file and add the HTML structure for the 'About Me' section to the `index.html` file, including a placeholder image and professional bio, to meet the subtask requirements.\n","\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"ea3907b6","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1772900626933,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":63,"user":{"displayName":"Nusrath Fathima","userId":"09146625910007660115"}},"outputId":"40f263bf-433e-4411-c27d-4c0522da8b44"},"source":["import os\n","\n","# Define CSS for the 'About Me' section\n","about_css = '''\n",".about-section {\n","    padding: 60px 20px;\n","    text-align: center;\n","    background-color: #ffffff;\n","}\n","\n",".about-section h2 {\n","    font-size: 2.5em;\n","    margin-bottom: 30px;\n","    color: #333;\n","}\n","\n",".about-content {\n","    display: flex;\n","    flex-direction: column;\n","    align-items: center;\n","    max-width: 900px;\n","    margin: 0 auto;\n","}\n","\n",".about-content img {\n","    width: 200px;\n","    height: 200px;\n","    border-radius: 50%;\n","    object-fit: cover;\n","    margin-bottom: 30px;\n","    border: 5px solid #007bff;\n","    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n","}\n","\n",".about-content p {\n","    font-size: 1.1em;\n","    line-height: 1.8;\n","    color: #555;\n","    text-align: justify;\n","    margin-bottom: 20px;\n","}\n","\n","/* Responsive adjustments */\n","@media (min-width: 768px) {\n","    .about-content {\n","        flex-direction: row;\n","        text-align: left;\n","    }\n","    .about-content img {\n","        margin-right: 40px;\n","        margin-bottom: 0;\n","    }\n","}\n","'''\n","\n","# Define HTML for the 'About Me' section\n","about_html = '''\n","    <section id=\"about\" class=\"about-section\">\n","        <h2>About Me</h2>\n","        <div class=\"about-content\">\n","            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/200/007bff/FFFFFF?text=Designer\" alt=\"Designer Profile\">\n","            <p>\n","                Hello! I'm a passionate freelance designer with over 10 years of experience in creating intuitive and stunning digital experiences. My expertise spans web design, UI/UX, and brand identity. I believe in a user-centered design approach, ensuring every project not only looks great but also functions seamlessly and meets client objectives. I'm always eager to take on new challenges and transform ideas into compelling visual realities.\n","            </p>\n","        </div>\n","    </section>\n","'''\n","\n","# Append CSS to style.css\n","style_css_path = os.path.join(project_dir, 'static', 'style.css')\n","with open(style_css_path, 'a') as f:\n","    f.write(about_css)\n","\n","print(f\"Appended 'About Me' section CSS to {style_css_path}\")\n","\n","# Read existing index.html content\n","index_html_path = os.path.join(project_dir, 'templates', 'index.html')\n","with open(index_html_path, 'r') as f:\n","    html_content = f.read()\n","\n","# Insert 'About Me' HTML before the closing </body> tag\n","if '</body>' in html_content:\n","    updated_html_content = html_content.replace('</body>', about_html + '\\n</body>')\n","else:\n","    updated_html_content = html_content + about_html # Fallback if no body tag (unlikely)\n","\n","# Write updated index.html\n","with open(index_html_path, 'w') as f:\n","    f.write(updated_html_content)\n","\n","print(f\"Appended 'About Me' section HTML to {index_html_path}\")"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Appended 'About Me' section CSS to flask_portfolio_app/static/style.css\n","Appended 'About Me' section HTML to flask_portfolio_app/templates/index.html\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"264d2599"},"source":["## Add Testimonials Section\n","\n","### Subtask:\n","Create the HTML and CSS for a testimonials section to feature client feedback, enhancing credibility.\n"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"363b4984"},"source":["**Reasoning**:\n","I will append the CSS rules for the testimonials section to the existing `style.css` file and add the HTML structure for the testimonials section to the `index.html` file, including placeholder testimonials, to meet the subtask requirements.\n","\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"ace79d97","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1772900654580,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":96,"user":{"displayName":"Nusrath Fathima","userId":"09146625910007660115"}},"outputId":"87af2fe1-221c-4153-f4b0-e6b8be2fd6cc"},"source":["import os\n","\n","# Define CSS for the testimonials section\n","testimonials_css = '''\n",".testimonials-section {\n","    padding: 60px 20px;\n","    text-align: center;\n","    background-color: #f0f2f5;\n","}\n","\n",".testimonials-section h2 {\n","    font-size: 2.5em;\n","    margin-bottom: 40px;\n","    color: #333;\n","}\n","\n",".testimonial-grid {\n","    display: grid;\n","    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n","    gap: 30px;\n","    max-width: 1200px;\n","    margin: 0 auto;\n","}\n","\n",".testimonial-item {\n","    background-color: white;\n","    border-radius: 8px;\n","    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n","    padding: 30px;\n","    text-align: center;\n","    transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n","}\n","\n",".testimonial-item:hover {\n","    transform: translateY(-5px);\n","}\n","\n",".testimonial-item img {\n","    width: 80px;\n","    height: 80px;\n","    border-radius: 50%;\n","    object-fit: cover;\n","    margin-bottom: 20px;\n","    border: 3px solid #007bff;\n","}\n","\n",".testimonial-item p {\n","    font-size: 1.1em;\n","    line-height: 1.6;\n","    color: #555;\n","    margin-bottom: 15px;\n","    font-style: italic;\n","}\n","\n",".testimonial-item h3 {\n","    font-size: 1.2em;\n","    color: #007bff;\n","    margin: 0;\n","}\n","\n","/* Responsive adjustments */\n","@media (max-width: 768px) {\n","    .testimonial-grid {\n","        grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n","    }\n","}\n","'''\n","\n","# Define HTML for the testimonials section\n","testimonials_html = '''\n","    <section class=\"testimonials-section\">\n","        <h2>What Clients Say</h2>\n","        <div class=\"testimonial-grid\">\n","            <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n","                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/80/007bff/FFFFFF?text=Client1\" alt=\"Client 1\">\n","                <p>\"The design work was outstanding! The designer truly understood our vision and delivered beyond our expectations. Highly recommended!\"</p>\n","                <h3>Jane Doe, CEO TechCo</h3>\n","            </div>\n","            <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n","                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/80/28a745/FFFFFF?text=Client2\" alt=\"Client 2\">\n","                <p>\"Professional, responsive, and incredibly talented. Our new website looks amazing and functions flawlessly. A pleasure to work with!\"</p>\n","                <h3>John Smith, Marketing Director</h3>\n","            </div>\n","            <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n","                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/80/ffc107/FFFFFF?text=Client3\" alt=\"Client 3\">\n","                <p>\"From concept to completion, the process was smooth and efficient. The attention to detail and creative input were exceptional.\"</p>\n","                <h3>Sarah Lee, Founder InnovateX</h3>\n","            </div>\n","        </div>\n","    </section>\n","'''\n","\n","# Append CSS to style.css\n","style_css_path = os.path.join(project_dir, 'static', 'style.css')\n","with open(style_css_path, 'a') as f:\n","    f.write(testimonials_css)\n","\n","print(f\"Appended testimonials section CSS to {style_css_path}\")\n","\n","# Read existing index.html content\n","index_html_path = os.path.join(project_dir, 'templates', 'index.html')\n","with open(index_html_path, 'r') as f:\n","    html_content = f.read()\n","\n","# Insert testimonials HTML before the closing </body> tag\n","if '</body>' in html_content:\n","    updated_html_content = html_content.replace('</body>', testimonials_html + '\\n</body>')\n","else:\n","    updated_html_content = html_content + testimonials_html # Fallback if no body tag (unlikely)\n","\n","# Write updated index.html\n","with open(index_html_path, 'w') as f:\n","    f.write(updated_html_content)\n","\n","print(f\"Appended testimonials section HTML to {index_html_path}\")"],"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["Appended